parsed_aggregateby = mongots.aggregateby.Aggregateby(1)
parse_aggregateby.return_value = parsed_aggregateby
build_unwind_and_match.return_value = []
self.mongots_collection.query(datetime(2001, 10, 2, 12), datetime(2002, 2, 
    3), aggregateby='1m', tags={'city': 'Paris'}, groupby=[])
parse_aggregateby.assert_called_with('1m')
build_unwind_and_match.assert_called_with(datetime(2001, 10, 2, 12),
    datetime(2002, 2, 3), parsed_aggregateby)
patch('mongots.collection.parse_aggregateby')patch('mongots.collection.build_unwind_and_match')
